By":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:01:54.000Z","msg":"救命呀，我比5毛圍<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1441386/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1441386/page/1</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一眼見晒連登5毛，快入快記錄<br />\n<br />\n由反對逃犯條例引發的風波持續，7月28日中上環衝突中，有44人被控暴動罪，其中一人為國泰航空機師。國泰航空今天回覆《香港01》查詢時指，根據該公司決定機師飛行職務的標準程序，該機師自7月15日起未執行任何飛行任務，而自7月30日起已沒有被安排飛行職務。<br />\n<br />\n另外，國泰航空指，有兩名機場員工因行為不當，已被解僱，據了解，他們是洩漏警員航班資料的地勤員工。"},{"pid":"13e4a6b5d4b904b854afb53d6bb395fb6c08dc54","tid":1441612,"uid":36008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:21:30.000Z","msg":"推到和理見到"},{"pid":"3f4587943a70862e42be8c0b65831b7e912430ac","tid":1441612,"uid":80851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:23:45.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"74dac7964f94559404eae35d2c01a0462e0321ed","tid":1441612,"uid":245353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:27:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"655dee6b157541494fe748e900c2876d7a27973d","tid":1441612,"uid":80851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:27:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c92f802ea4de72eb4310db1b5d4d9b79ba1f296","tid":1441612,"uid":80851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:28:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc0d5a4030658cb32e8ec5dcdadd3c3b0aead42c","tid":1441612,"uid":80851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:28:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01b6769c4051283e4eecfdb96c940df212dc372c","tid":1441612,"uid":245353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:28:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cf20adc14433d1da06430554fc7b799dd664cb3f","